{
  "name": "ControlFormat",
  "summary": "<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例为第一张工作表上的列表框控件设置填充区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListFillRange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表上第二个形状（组合框）的所有数据项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RemoveAllItems</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>包含 ET 控件 （ET 控件：ET 本身具有的控件，而不是 ActiveX 控件。）属性。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Shape/Shape .htm#Shape.ControlFormat\">ControlFormat</a></strong> 属性可返回 <strong>ControlFormat</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>如果指定的形状不是控件，则 <strong>ControlFormat</strong> 属性失效；并且如果该控件不是列表框，则 <strong>ListFillRange</strong> 属性失效。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "DropDownLines",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置组合框中下拉区域中显示的列表行的数目。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个组合框，并将其下拉部分设置为 10 行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlDropDown, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DropDownLines</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（组合框）中下拉区域中显示的列表行的数目。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DropDownLines</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Enabled",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果启用对象，则为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表的第一个形状设置成禁用。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Enabled</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（组合框）是否启用对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Enabled</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "LargeChange",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>滚动一页时，返回或设置滚动框增加或减少的量（当用户单击滚动条时）。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个滚动条，并设置其链接单元格、最大值、最小值、大步长值和小步长值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlScrollBar, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LinkedCell</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Max</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Min</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LargeChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SmallChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第三个形状（滚动条）的大步长值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LargeChange</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "LinkedCell",
      "summary": "<p>不能将该属性应用于多选列表框。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指向控制值的工作表区域。如果为这些单元格赋值，则指定控制也会取得相应的值。与此类似，如果更改控制的值，则单元格的值也作相应变动。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例为第一张工作表添加复选框，并将 A1 单元格设置为此复选框的附属单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlCheckBox, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LinkedCell</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第三个形状（滚动条）链接单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LinkedCell</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ListCount",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回列表框或者组合框中数据项的数目。如果列表中没有数据项，则返回 0（零）。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对组合框进行调整，使其可以显示列表中的所有数据项。如果第一个形状不代表组合框，则本示例无效。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DropDownLines</span> = controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListCount</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（列表框）数据项的数目。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListCount</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ListFillRange",
      "summary": "<p>ET 阅读区域中的每一单元格的内容，并将单元格值插入到列表框中。列表对该区域中单元格的修订进行追踪。</p>\n<p>如果列表框中的列表是使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ControlFormat/ControlFormat .htm#ControlFormat.AddItem\">AddItem</a></strong> 方法创建的，则此属性返回一个空字符串 (&quot;&quot;)。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置用于填充指定列表框的工作表区域。对该属性进行设置将破坏列表框中的所有列表项。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将列表框添加到第一张工作表中，并为该列表框设置填充区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlListBox, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListFillRange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状（列表框）的填充区域。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListFillRange</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ListIndex",
      "summary": "<p>不能将该属性应用于多选列表框。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置列表框或组合框中当前选定项的索引号。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除列表框中选定的数据项。如果 `Shapes.Item(2)` 代表的不是列表框，则本示例将无效。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RemoveItem</span>(controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListIndex</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第一个形状（列表框）当前选定项的索引号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListIndex</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "LockedText",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>当工作簿受保护时，指定对象中的文字是否被锁定以免发生更改，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表的第一个形状（组合框）的文字锁定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LockedText</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（列表框）的文字是否被锁定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LockedText</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Max",
      "summary": "<p><strong>Max</strong> 属性的值必须大于 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ControlFormat/ControlFormat .htm#ControlFormat.Min\">Min</a></strong> 属性的值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置滚动条或微调控制项区域的最大值。滚动条或微调控制项的值不会超过指定的最大值。可读写 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个滚动条，并设置其链接单元格、最大值、最小值、大步长值和小步长值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlScrollBar, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LinkedCell</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Max</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Min</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LargeChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SmallChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第三个形状（滚动条）的最大值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Max</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Min",
      "summary": "<p><strong>Min</strong> 属性的值必须小于 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ControlFormat/ControlFormat .htm#ControlFormat.Max\">Max</a></strong> 属性的值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置滚动条或微调控制项区域的最小值。滚动条或微调控制项的值不会小于指定的最小值。可读写 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个滚动条，并设置其链接单元格、最大值、最小值、大步长值和小步长值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlScrollBar, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LinkedCell</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Max</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Min</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LargeChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SmallChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第三个形状（滚动条）的最小值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Min</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MultiSelect",
      "summary": "<p>如果为单项选择 (<strong>xlNone</strong>)，则每次只允许选择一项。单击鼠标或按空格键将取消原先的选择项，并选定正在单击的项。</p>\n<p>如果为简单的多项选择 (<strong>xlSimple</strong>)，当用鼠标单击选定某选项，或在突出显示选项上按空格键时，可切换该选项的选定状态，此方式适用于经常需要选定多个选项的列表。</p>\n<p>如果为扩展多项选择 (<strong>xlExtended</strong>)，其作用与单项选择列表框一样，单击某选项将选定该选项并取消选定其他选项。按住 Shift 单击鼠标或按箭头键，可从当前选项开始顺序选定多个选项。按住 Ctrl 单击选项，可在选定项集合中添加选中项。此方式适用于允许多项选择但又不经常使用的列表。</p>\n<p>可使用 <strong>Value</strong> 属性或 <strong>ListIndex</strong> 属性返回或设置单项选择列表框的选定项。</p>\n<p>不能使用 <strong>LinkedCell</strong> 属性对多项选择列表框进行链接。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定列表框的选择模式。可为以下常量之一：<strong>xlNone</strong>、<strong>xlSimple</strong> 或 <strong>xlExtended</strong>。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个简单多项选择列表框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlListBox, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MultiSelect</span> = xlSimple\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（列表框）的选择模式是否为单项选择。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MultiSelect</span> == xlNone)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PrintObject",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果打印文档时也打印指定对象，则为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表的第一个形状设置为打印文档时不打印该对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintObject</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（列表框）打印文档时是否打印该对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintObject</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SmallChange",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置滚动条或微调框在滚动一行（当用户单击箭头）时的增量或减量。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个滚动条，并设置其链接单元格、最大值、最小值、大步长值和小步长值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlScrollBar, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LinkedCell</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D1&quot;</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Max</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Min</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LargeChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SmallChange</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第三个形状（滚动条）的小步长值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SmallChange</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表指定的控件格式的值。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表的第一个形状（组合框）的 Value 属性设置为1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状（列表框）选定的数据项的编号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "AddItem",
      "summary": "<p>使用本方法可清除由 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ControlFormat/ControlFormat .htm#ControlFormat.ListFillRange\">ListFillRange</a></strong> 属性指定的任何区域。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>为列表框或组合框添加项。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个列表框并用 1 到 10 的整数对其进行填充。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlListBox, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> x = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; x &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; x++) {\n        shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddItem</span>(x)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个组合框并按照指定索引对其进行填充。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddFormControl</span>(xlDropDown, <span class=\"hljs-number\">500</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">110</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">110</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddItem</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddItem</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Text",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "<p>要添加的文本。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>新输入项的位置。如果列表中输入项数目少于指定索引，则将列表末尾的空白项目添加到指定位置。如果省略该参数，则将项目追加到现有列表。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "RemoveAllItems",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除 ET 列表框或组合框中的所有数据项。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除一个列表框中的所有数据项。如果 `Shapes.Item(2)` 代表的不是列表框，则本示例将无效。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RemoveAllItems</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表上第一个形状（组合框）的所有数据项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RemoveAllItems</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "RemoveItem",
      "summary": "<p>如果指定对象定义了填充区域，则该方法无效。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ControlFormat/ControlFormat .htm#ControlFormat.RemoveAllItems\">RemoveAllItems</a></strong> 方法删除 ET 列表框或组合框中的所有数据项。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>从列表框或组合框中删除一个或多个数据项。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除列表框中选定的数据项。如果 `Shapes.Item(2)` 代表的不是列表框，则本示例将无效。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> controlFormat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>\n    controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RemoveItem</span>(controlFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ListIndex</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例删除活动工作表的第一个形状（列表框）的两个数据项，从索引1开始。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ControlFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">RemoveItem</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int4 精度）",
          "description": "<p>第一个要删除的数据项编号。有效值为从 1 到列表中的数据项数目（<strong>ListCount</strong> 属性返回的值）。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "Count",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>要删除的数据项数目，从 <em>Index</em> 项开始。如果省略该参数，则只删除一个数据项。如果 <em>Index</em> + <em>Count</em> 超过列表中的数据项数目，则删除列表中从 <em>Index</em> 项到最后一项的所有数据项并且不报错。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}